profile:
Eddie has been in this industry since 2013. While attending GBC [casa loma]; Eddie worked as a handyman \ serviceman for an established company. He quickly realized that he loved and enjoyed meeting new clients on a daily. Handling their requests, bringing them satisfaction and joy, simply putting a smile on their faces from work well done was very rewarding. However all the hard work, personal sacrifices, and satisfied clients, etc., was all for the benefit of the company and not Eddie. That is when Eddie got inspired to open up his own company, and EAVES BY EDDIE was born. 
We install, maintain, clean, repair, unblock gutters and downpipes for the best price, while providing clients with top quality service at all times. Any other services you may require, please don't be hesitant to ask; we are willing to assist you in any way possible that we can!

profile:
Gateway Roofing & Contracting Ltd is dedicated to providing the best service and they do everything they can to make sure you are completely satisfied with the work provided. Using the latest industry-approved practices to reinforce vulnerable and weak areas so your home is protected long after the work is done. 
 
Asphalt shingles may be their specialty but they are also experienced in eavestrough, soffit, fascia, siding, attic insulation & venting, skylights and much more. A harsh climate, bad architectural design, inadequate roof ventilation and lack of insulation can disrupt the function of your home causing roofing and waterproofing products to break down prematurely. They will identify these issues, educate you with a proper solution and provide a written estimate.
